burlap.behavior.singleagent.learning.lspi

Class SARSData

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learning.lspi.SARSData

  • public class SARSData
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that provides a wrapper for a List holding a bunch of state-action-reward-state (SARSData.SARS) tuples. The dataset is backed by an ArrayList.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
